{"tid":2221833,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［港大流出］［原片無碼］港男黑人混戰（多圖有片 圖文並茂）","createTime":"2020-09-28T16:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T04:54:54.000Z","uid":292129,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d7e03f83dbfa325b03389eaa09b4ac05c74f17","tid":2221833,"uid":292129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:03:01.000Z","msg":"原片無碼：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100038531136264/posts/323782028916166/?extid=5TMjDDYCGOcCnZNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100038531136264%2Fposts%2F323782028916166%2F%3Fextid%3D5TMjDDYCGOcCnZNs&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=912c668b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100038531136264/posts/323782028916166/?extid=5TMjDDYCGOcCnZNs</a><br />\n<br />\n故事由一班撕紙狗開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hu4Ydhz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHu4Ydhz.png&h=ebe37ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjOidhB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjOidhB.png&h=06e50939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZg7Q4j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZg7Q4j.png&h=c8224517&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n無讀嘅書嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於入到港大，緊係好興奮狗衝咁撕撕撕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQdVfv3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQdVfv3.png&h=d6781148&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n「感到恐懼、自責、內疚、後悔、絕望 唔應該係抗爭手足，而應該係暴力政權中每一位既得利益者」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSF8AwA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSF8AwA.png&h=ea3ea0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後亦難逃魔掌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWGS2bH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWGS2bH.png&h=16973d22&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n白衫保安表示我睇唔到（設計對白）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8rvORK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8rvORK.png&h=82913311&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（人強馬壯的港大保安團隊）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBYx2fK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBYx2fK.jpg&h=83e29af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係！最最最後竟然俾我哋發現保安手足！！！<br />\n片段中前線保安手足居然舉起🤚🏻👍🏻黃金手勢，護送在場人士離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇睇下又好似有啲似曾相識喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76ZtABk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76ZtABk.png&h=d58e08ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面原圖挑戰連登p圖高手：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Up6chLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUp6chLb.jpg&h=16981d20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d856821eb6a3be8584fb7a501ada5acae72b3868","tid":2221833,"uid":292129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c482273097f4212a244234719871c55de1b71ab","tid":2221833,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4de8afc7591aeb6e2e2ce9854fc5da432937256a","tid":2221833,"uid":4239,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解2020年 D片都係咁高清？"},{"pid":"6feb11cc7f096082fb1caf4214b8716570bfb979","tid":2221833,"uid":347404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a529dd6225ae4116cf2a3e4bdf935edee642fe92","tid":2221833,"uid":325243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":